# liblouis: Elfdalian 8-Dot Braille Table Based on Swedish 8-Dot Braille
#
#-name: Älvdalska 8-punkts fullskrift
#-index-name: Elfdalian, 8-dot braille
#-display-name: Elfdalian 8-dot braille
#
#  Copyright (C) 2022-2026 Insyn Scandinavia AB <david@insyn.se>
